WEBVTT

01:51.630 --> 01:57.500
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.640 --> 02:01.950
[Episode 12]

02:08.840 --> 02:10.039
Where's that fellow?

02:10.720 --> 02:11.320
Who?

02:12.050 --> 02:13.090
You know who.

02:15.520 --> 02:17.450
He left first thing in the morning.

02:18.590 --> 02:20.079
After you finish your breakfast,

02:20.079 --> 02:22.320
Your Excellency, please leave promptly.

02:22.320 --> 02:23.550
You came here once,

02:23.790 --> 02:25.920
and already guzzled up

02:25.940 --> 02:27.970
all of my aged wine.

02:28.000 --> 02:29.150
If you come a couple more times,

02:29.150 --> 02:31.690
I... I really
wouldn't be able to handle it.

02:33.190 --> 02:33.960
Lord Fan.

02:34.650 --> 02:36.550
I did drink too much last night.

02:36.610 --> 02:37.680
But don't worry.

02:37.870 --> 02:38.870
Once I get back,

02:38.870 --> 02:40.190
I'll arrange for your wine to be replaced.

02:40.190 --> 02:41.790
I promise it'll be good wine.

02:42.079 --> 02:44.010
The wine is secondary.

02:44.829 --> 02:47.320
Your Excellency,
since you and my daughter divorced,

02:47.320 --> 02:49.650
our family's been facing much criticism.

02:50.310 --> 02:52.840
You showing up at our residence

02:53.760 --> 02:56.780
might damage her reputation.

02:57.270 --> 02:58.870
Please forgive me, Lord Fan.

02:59.640 --> 03:01.040
I have my reasons.

03:01.060 --> 03:03.260
Can I have a word with Fan Yun in private?

03:04.280 --> 03:05.240
Absolutely

03:05.760 --> 03:06.450
not.

03:11.320 --> 03:12.320
Your Excellency,

03:12.430 --> 03:13.380
whatever it is,

03:13.400 --> 03:14.600
just say it straight.

03:15.120 --> 03:16.150
There is nothing

03:16.150 --> 03:17.960
my father and Gao Ran can't know.

03:17.990 --> 03:18.740
Speak.

03:30.060 --> 03:30.990
Alright then.

03:33.470 --> 03:34.150
Fan Yun,

03:34.760 --> 03:36.410
since we divorced, I've been

03:37.160 --> 03:38.090
thinking of you.

03:40.650 --> 03:41.190
You...

03:41.210 --> 03:44.230
Thinking of how you must be
studying at home all day long.

03:44.230 --> 03:46.450
But you have no experience as an official.

03:46.450 --> 03:49.079
Even if you pass the selection exam,
you lack the credibility

03:49.079 --> 03:51.280
to be entrusted with
heavy responsibilities.

03:51.280 --> 03:52.160
So I want you...

03:54.160 --> 03:54.880
Dad!

03:54.910 --> 03:56.000
Go on, Your Excellency.

03:56.000 --> 03:57.000
So I want you to

03:57.000 --> 03:57.890
move into my residence

03:57.890 --> 03:59.750
and train at the Commerce Bureau.

04:01.600 --> 04:03.010
That's great, Your Excellency.

04:03.010 --> 04:04.970
You finally remembered this.

04:04.990 --> 04:06.220
I never forgot it!

04:07.410 --> 04:08.640
Don't give me that.

04:09.010 --> 04:10.640
Since I left your residence,

04:11.130 --> 04:12.930
I've been waiting for your news.

04:13.120 --> 04:14.030
But

04:14.030 --> 04:15.520
the things you sent over

04:15.970 --> 04:18.500
were either irrelevant letters

04:18.600 --> 04:20.760
or some odd gifts.

04:21.250 --> 04:22.850
They're nothing but a waste.

04:23.460 --> 04:25.410
How can gifts for you be a waste?

04:25.440 --> 04:26.170
Well...

04:28.420 --> 04:30.100
Have you read those letters?

04:30.670 --> 04:31.340
I...

04:31.600 --> 04:32.550
I've read them.

04:33.400 --> 04:35.250
On such premium paper,

04:35.280 --> 04:37.870
you only wrote one line per letter.

04:37.950 --> 04:39.500
And the contents were so strange.

04:39.500 --> 04:40.540
Like,

04:40.580 --> 04:41.960
"It rained today,

04:42.300 --> 04:44.500
and the carp in the pond are energetic."

04:44.570 --> 04:45.790
And what...

04:46.110 --> 04:48.180
"Though I'm in the depths of solitude,

04:48.180 --> 04:50.690
I can go to bed alone."

04:50.960 --> 04:53.080
What kind of nonsense is that?

04:53.100 --> 04:54.830
-It was all...
-It was Wei Ying!

04:55.400 --> 04:56.940
Wei Ying told me to write them.

04:56.940 --> 04:58.940
He said
the more letters I wrote, the better.

04:58.940 --> 05:00.870
Isn't the content more important?

05:01.730 --> 05:02.930
What about the gifts?

05:02.930 --> 05:03.990
Did you get the ice?

05:04.840 --> 05:05.840
I made shaved ice

05:05.860 --> 05:07.000
for the kids.

05:07.160 --> 05:08.100
What about the boiled eggs?

05:08.100 --> 05:09.030
You told me

05:09.060 --> 05:10.460
they were your favorite.

05:10.750 --> 05:12.550
I shared them with my neighbors.

05:13.280 --> 05:14.410
And the red flowers!

05:14.610 --> 05:16.010
You must have loved them.

05:16.310 --> 05:18.370
I pressed them in a book as specimens.

05:19.600 --> 05:21.120
And the bronze figurine of me?

05:21.120 --> 05:23.520
It's displayed in the house as decoration.

05:27.390 --> 05:29.180
That was the governor?

05:29.200 --> 05:31.930
I thought it was a talisman
to scare the evil away.

05:32.450 --> 05:34.350
The governor's craftsmanship is poor,

05:34.350 --> 05:36.170
but his heart is sincere.

05:37.690 --> 05:39.570
You just noticed?

05:42.700 --> 05:43.550
Yes,

05:43.570 --> 05:46.250
I just noticed
you have food in your teeth.

05:52.440 --> 05:53.440
Your Excellency,

05:54.590 --> 05:56.700
I strongly oppose

05:56.730 --> 05:58.550
Yun moving back into the Qi Residence.

05:58.550 --> 06:00.280
Since she's already left,

06:00.310 --> 06:02.900
why go back and humiliate herself?

06:04.200 --> 06:05.260
-Lord Fan Qi.
-Dad.

06:06.890 --> 06:08.540
Fan Yun aspires to be an official

06:08.540 --> 06:09.980
who serves the people.

06:10.580 --> 06:12.130
I've done everything I could

06:12.130 --> 06:13.300
to clear the obstacles for her.

06:13.300 --> 06:14.560
Please grant her wish.

06:15.030 --> 06:16.830
Even if I agree,

06:18.090 --> 06:19.030
Yun would

06:19.150 --> 06:20.830
never agree to it.

06:21.680 --> 06:22.390
Dad,

06:22.860 --> 06:23.780
I agree.

06:26.290 --> 06:29.500
Yes, Yun agreed,

06:29.530 --> 06:32.320
but Gao Ran would absolutely not agree.

06:34.120 --> 06:35.070
I...

06:36.190 --> 06:37.240
agree too.

06:39.750 --> 06:41.210
Anyone else in the family?

06:41.320 --> 06:41.850
I...

06:42.630 --> 06:44.510
We also have a cat.

06:45.890 --> 06:47.110
Dad!

06:47.380 --> 06:48.110
But...

06:49.040 --> 06:50.870
But disguising as a man

06:50.890 --> 06:53.010
is easy to see through.

06:55.200 --> 06:57.280
With Fan Yun's figure...

06:59.500 --> 07:01.850
Wow, she looks just like a boy.

07:08.930 --> 07:11.170
I don't know if I should be happy or sad,

07:11.750 --> 07:13.280
or just beat you fellows up.

07:13.940 --> 07:15.330
Yun, it's summer again,

07:15.350 --> 07:17.440
your least favorite season.

07:19.230 --> 07:20.150
Fan Yun,

07:20.170 --> 07:21.100
good luck.

07:21.130 --> 07:22.220
Once you enter the Commerce Bureau,

07:22.220 --> 07:23.830
you can do what you love most.

07:27.650 --> 07:35.050
[Be Discreet in Word and Deed]

07:48.970 --> 07:50.630
Greetings, Your Excellency.

07:50.750 --> 07:52.070
Greetings, Your Excellency.

07:52.070 --> 07:52.920
Carry on.

07:57.330 --> 07:58.380
Lord Jiang.

07:59.200 --> 08:00.550
I've brought you

08:00.980 --> 08:02.920
the person I recommended yesterday.

08:02.920 --> 08:04.300
Please train him well.

08:04.610 --> 08:06.870
I'm Fan Xiu.
Nice to meet you, Lord Jiang.

08:07.360 --> 08:08.360
Your Excellency.

08:09.190 --> 08:11.520
The Commerce Bureau
can't accept Fan Yun.

08:13.680 --> 08:15.510
-What?
-You could tell at a glance?

08:15.510 --> 08:17.710
Ordinary people naturally can't tell,

08:18.490 --> 08:20.290
but I'm a medical practitioner.

08:21.070 --> 08:23.750
I never perceive people
just by their appearance.

08:23.750 --> 08:25.930
No matter how well she disguises herself,

08:25.930 --> 08:27.400
I can still tell.

08:28.800 --> 08:29.830
Lord Jiang,

08:29.850 --> 08:32.270
since you can perceive me
through my disguise,

08:32.270 --> 08:34.510
you must also see my sincerity.

08:34.970 --> 08:36.100
Please let me

08:36.340 --> 08:37.940
stay in the Commerce Bureau.

08:39.390 --> 08:40.590
Since ancient times,

08:41.080 --> 08:43.539
there have never been
any female officials.

08:43.640 --> 08:45.640
My Commerce Bureau is no exception.

08:45.900 --> 08:46.590
Lord Jiang,

08:47.060 --> 08:49.120
please give me this chance. I...

08:49.150 --> 08:51.850
This precedent can't be set
in my Commerce Bureau.

08:51.850 --> 08:54.130
Even for someone
recommended by Your Excellency,

08:54.130 --> 08:55.530
there are no exceptions.

08:56.120 --> 08:57.210
Say no more.

08:57.570 --> 08:58.860
Please go back.

09:00.140 --> 09:01.140
Don't be anxious.

09:01.300 --> 09:02.210
I'll handle it.

09:03.750 --> 09:04.350
Come here.

09:05.020 --> 09:06.290
In front of all these people,

09:06.290 --> 09:08.090
can't you respect my authority?

09:11.060 --> 09:12.340
Lord Jiang, listen up.

09:13.020 --> 09:15.050
You violated medical ethics
and deceived me, the governor,

09:15.050 --> 09:16.610
and slandered the late governor.

09:16.610 --> 09:19.740
Do you know the consequences
of these 3 crimes combined?

09:20.680 --> 09:21.800
You found out?

09:21.820 --> 09:22.950
I found out long ago!

09:24.980 --> 09:26.740
If you accept Fan Yun now,

09:27.720 --> 09:29.120
I'll let you off the hook.

09:29.350 --> 09:30.210
What do you say?

09:32.430 --> 09:33.140
Hurry up.

09:37.050 --> 09:37.810
You...

09:41.740 --> 09:42.870
Changing your mask

09:42.870 --> 09:45.130
doesn't fool me.
I see right through you.

09:46.050 --> 09:47.880
Your eyes have betrayed you.

09:47.940 --> 09:49.200
I'll take that as a yes.

09:53.200 --> 09:54.080
Hurry up!

09:55.360 --> 09:57.160
Since Your Excellency insists,

09:57.650 --> 09:59.010
he can stay on probation

09:59.040 --> 10:00.280
for two days.

10:02.850 --> 10:03.680
Really?

10:04.390 --> 10:05.170
Wonderful!

10:05.410 --> 10:06.670
Thank you, Lord Jiang!

10:08.570 --> 10:09.860
However, if it turns out

10:09.860 --> 10:11.500
that the hardships of officialdom

10:11.500 --> 10:12.860
are too much to bear for you

10:12.860 --> 10:13.920
and you want to leave,

10:13.920 --> 10:15.400
I am not to blame.

10:16.000 --> 10:17.210
In this bureau,

10:18.150 --> 10:19.880
your abilities are what count.

10:20.600 --> 10:22.120
Please rest assured, Lord Jiang.

10:22.120 --> 10:22.930
Don't worry.

10:23.630 --> 10:25.290
Fan Xiu will work his hardest.

10:37.130 --> 10:38.130
Your Excellency.

10:38.920 --> 10:40.540
Say, why does

10:40.970 --> 10:43.060
Lord Jiang wear a mask?

10:43.090 --> 10:45.930
He looks so mysterious and unapproachable.

10:48.280 --> 10:50.210
Because he's not as handsome as me.

10:51.870 --> 10:52.710
Just kidding.

10:53.000 --> 10:53.950
That fellow

10:54.260 --> 10:56.110
has always been a bit eccentric.

10:56.130 --> 10:57.070
But he is a good person.

10:57.070 --> 10:58.040
Don't worry.

11:00.660 --> 11:02.300
How did you

11:02.320 --> 11:03.200
make him agree?

11:03.910 --> 11:05.310
I govern the Nine Cities.

11:05.740 --> 11:07.400
Who has the gall to disobey me?

11:07.670 --> 11:08.720
Except you.

11:11.030 --> 11:11.630
Alright.

11:12.480 --> 11:14.340
Work hard at the Commerce Bureau.

11:15.320 --> 11:16.910
Thank you, Your Excellency.

11:16.910 --> 11:17.370
I'm off.

11:32.960 --> 11:34.690
Since it's your first day here,

11:34.930 --> 11:36.320
I'll give you less work.

11:37.190 --> 11:38.570
Please give your orders, Lord Jiang.

11:38.570 --> 11:41.360
Organize these records by date,

11:41.790 --> 11:43.590
and send them to Qilin Pavilion.

11:43.630 --> 11:46.090
Organize the books
in this bookcase as well.

11:46.590 --> 11:48.720
And classify
the discarded documents

11:49.480 --> 11:50.550
opposite.

11:51.510 --> 11:52.270
Also,

11:52.750 --> 11:54.270
return a few books

11:54.600 --> 11:56.120
and borrow some new ones.

11:58.400 --> 11:59.480
And this.

12:00.510 --> 12:01.640
Take this register,

12:01.880 --> 12:04.560
and go to relay this
to the head of the Rites Bureau:

12:04.560 --> 12:07.090
"Proposing such a ridiculous
annual budget,

12:07.150 --> 12:09.080
did you leave your brains at home?"

12:09.780 --> 12:10.460
Remember to

12:10.620 --> 12:12.620
relay it word for word.

12:14.150 --> 12:15.440
Any questions?

12:17.030 --> 12:17.670
No.

12:18.160 --> 12:19.040
No questions.

12:20.100 --> 12:21.500
Don't mess anything up.

12:22.270 --> 12:23.040
But

12:23.080 --> 12:24.170
Lord Jiang,

12:24.360 --> 12:25.280
what if...

12:25.960 --> 12:27.860
what if I accidentally make a mistake?

12:27.860 --> 12:29.530
That would be perfect.

12:29.560 --> 12:31.610
Then I can legitimately kick you out

12:31.720 --> 12:33.050
of the Commerce Bureau.

12:33.610 --> 12:35.370
You're here to help,

12:35.720 --> 12:37.030
not to cause trouble.

12:37.550 --> 12:39.390
I'm short-handed here.

12:39.840 --> 12:42.770
I don't have the time
to teach others how to do things.

12:43.040 --> 12:43.920
Yes.

12:43.940 --> 12:45.220
I'll go right away.

12:46.970 --> 12:47.970
Right away.

13:02.720 --> 13:03.850
I have to say,

13:03.880 --> 13:05.810
we really underestimated Fan Yun.

13:06.110 --> 13:07.000
I heard she's been

13:07.000 --> 13:08.660
working day and night lately.

13:08.970 --> 13:09.970
Her drive is just

13:10.000 --> 13:11.730
like the blazing sun overhead,

13:12.960 --> 13:15.560
not something
an ordinary man can match at all.

13:15.990 --> 13:16.870
I know.

13:16.890 --> 13:18.820
She was the governor's wife,

13:19.620 --> 13:21.820
and now she's cross-dressing to study.

13:22.900 --> 13:23.620
Say, what is

13:23.650 --> 13:24.980
the governor thinking,

13:25.270 --> 13:26.890
assigning her to the Commerce Bureau

13:26.890 --> 13:29.300
and making her
Lord Jiang's personal errand girl?

13:29.300 --> 13:31.700
Lord Jiang is unmatched in his shrewdness,

13:31.730 --> 13:33.530
capability, and eccentricity.

13:33.850 --> 13:35.030
I'm afraid this year

13:35.030 --> 13:36.690
will be a tough one for Fan Yun.

13:38.690 --> 13:40.090
Do you think the governor

13:40.490 --> 13:41.820
will feel sorry for her?

13:42.150 --> 13:43.440
The governor's been busy

13:43.440 --> 13:44.970
dealing with the Three Elders.

13:44.970 --> 13:46.770
I doubt he has time to feel sorry.

13:47.340 --> 13:48.810
But I realized...

13:50.730 --> 13:51.660
you finally know

13:52.010 --> 13:53.670
a thing or two about feelings.

13:55.440 --> 13:56.840
Do you have nothing to do?

13:57.120 --> 13:58.120
I'm going to work.

14:05.500 --> 14:06.450
Wei Ying!

14:08.690 --> 14:10.290
Who blocked off the doorway?

14:13.240 --> 14:14.550
Over there.

14:17.860 --> 14:19.320
I don't need you to tell me!

14:41.730 --> 14:42.330
Fan Yun.

14:43.250 --> 14:44.170
Gao Ran?

14:44.240 --> 14:45.460
Why are you still up?

14:45.770 --> 14:47.900
You haven't rested since you got back.

14:47.970 --> 14:50.430
At least eat something
before you continue.

14:53.040 --> 14:54.440
Chicken legs!

14:55.280 --> 14:56.130
Gao Ran,

14:56.160 --> 14:57.310
you're the best.

14:57.330 --> 14:58.480
I'm starving.

14:58.710 --> 14:59.350
Slow down.

15:00.600 --> 15:01.860
You're eating so fast.

15:02.080 --> 15:03.670
Have you not eaten all day?

15:04.730 --> 15:06.330
Yes, I haven't eaten all day.

15:06.480 --> 15:07.310
Right now,

15:07.790 --> 15:10.370
I'm constantly worried
others will find out I'm a woman.

15:10.370 --> 15:11.550
So before I'm exposed,

15:11.550 --> 15:14.210
I want to learn more
and get more hands-on experience,

15:14.210 --> 15:15.270
so all this anxiety

15:15.500 --> 15:17.270
wouldn't be for nothing,

15:17.300 --> 15:18.230
don't you think?

15:18.870 --> 15:19.870
So,

15:19.870 --> 15:21.090
you must be confident.

15:21.090 --> 15:22.070
You can do it, Fan Yun.

15:22.070 --> 15:22.770
I'm leaving.

15:22.770 --> 15:23.770
Be confident?

15:24.900 --> 15:26.260
Con... Con...

15:27.290 --> 15:28.170
Gao Ran!

15:28.580 --> 15:30.570
What confidence are you talking about?

15:30.570 --> 15:31.260
You...

15:31.930 --> 15:34.070
[Hualin Gate]

15:37.010 --> 15:37.980
Young man.

15:38.870 --> 15:39.870
Young man!

15:41.480 --> 15:42.080
Young man.

15:42.960 --> 15:44.840
My Lord, are you calling me?

15:45.280 --> 15:46.740
Of course I'm calling you.

15:49.440 --> 15:50.670
I heard that

15:50.670 --> 15:53.280
a smart and capable young man
has joined the Commerce Bureau.

15:53.280 --> 15:54.490
That must be you.

15:55.720 --> 15:56.720
What's your name?

15:57.840 --> 15:58.550
My Lord,

15:58.580 --> 15:59.580
I'm...

16:00.370 --> 16:01.440
I'm...

16:01.470 --> 16:02.110
Fan Xiu!

16:03.750 --> 16:04.710
Fan Xiu.

16:07.050 --> 16:08.330
Lord Jiang

16:08.350 --> 16:10.110
has always been very strict.

16:10.140 --> 16:11.810
Working under him

16:11.910 --> 16:13.110
must be tough, right?

16:13.480 --> 16:14.240
Not at all.

16:14.480 --> 16:15.990
I actually quite like it.

16:16.630 --> 16:18.760
Strict teachers make great students.

16:20.080 --> 16:21.390
Good, good.

16:22.120 --> 16:23.390
A formidable youth.

16:25.390 --> 16:26.920
I still don't know

16:27.240 --> 16:29.000
who you are, My Lord.

16:30.000 --> 16:31.320
I'm your...

16:31.620 --> 16:32.740
well...

16:33.730 --> 16:35.060
I think

16:35.540 --> 16:37.690
you're about the same age as my son.

16:38.260 --> 16:40.620
Why don't you just call me Uncle?

16:41.720 --> 16:44.120
Unc... Uncle?

16:45.550 --> 16:46.480
Uncle.

16:47.320 --> 16:48.550
Uncle?

16:53.310 --> 16:53.850
By the way,

16:53.850 --> 16:56.490
I need to return documents
to the Rites Bureau.

16:56.550 --> 16:58.000
I-I... See you.

16:58.330 --> 16:59.130
See you.

17:01.090 --> 17:02.230
When you see me around,

17:02.230 --> 17:03.780
remember to call me Uncle!

17:05.069 --> 17:06.589
Uncle, Uncle.

17:07.010 --> 17:09.810
People sure love
claiming family ties these days.

17:22.510 --> 17:23.510
Lord Jiang.

17:24.609 --> 17:25.480
Lord Jiang,

17:25.510 --> 17:27.890
these are the official documents
processed yesterday.

17:27.890 --> 17:29.020
Please review them.

17:39.750 --> 17:41.510
Ever since the governor ordered

17:41.510 --> 17:44.970
the implementation
of tax reduction and exemption policies,

17:45.750 --> 17:48.220
the treasury's been more depleted
than in previous years.

17:48.220 --> 17:50.000
We have no way to increase revenue.

17:50.000 --> 17:50.660
Does anyone

17:51.430 --> 17:52.960
have any good suggestions?

17:53.720 --> 17:54.800
In my opinion,

17:55.260 --> 17:57.910
local subsidies can be
moderately scaled back.

17:57.910 --> 17:58.560
Right.

17:58.580 --> 17:59.880
With less tax collected,

17:59.880 --> 18:02.080
local expenditures should be reduced.

18:03.350 --> 18:03.990
Fan Xiu,

18:04.720 --> 18:05.970
any ideas?

18:08.010 --> 18:08.770
My Lord,

18:10.000 --> 18:11.720
if it were up to me...

18:13.510 --> 18:15.350
I'd instead allocate special funds

18:15.350 --> 18:17.880
to establish
a comprehensive subsidy system

18:18.110 --> 18:19.610
to make good use of every penny.

18:19.610 --> 18:20.940
That's inappropriate.

18:21.340 --> 18:22.170
Fan Xiu,

18:22.910 --> 18:25.010
we need to cut expenses
even with increased revenue,

18:25.010 --> 18:28.170
let alone when the treasury
is emptier than before.

18:28.270 --> 18:29.580
Are you in your right mind?

18:29.580 --> 18:30.470
Exactly.

18:30.560 --> 18:31.420
We need to cut expenses,

18:31.420 --> 18:33.150
not empty the treasury faster.

18:34.760 --> 18:35.600
Fan Xiu,

18:35.920 --> 18:37.650
explain your rationale first.

18:40.590 --> 18:41.720
With lighter taxes,

18:41.920 --> 18:43.030
the people should be

18:43.030 --> 18:45.560
more willing to
reclaim land and plant crops,

18:45.960 --> 18:47.090
or even do business.

18:48.110 --> 18:49.750
But from the look of things now,

18:49.750 --> 18:51.780
there's been no sign of improvement.

18:51.780 --> 18:53.280
This is because the people are

18:53.280 --> 18:54.810
still in observation mode.

18:55.110 --> 18:55.810
Lord Jiang,

18:56.270 --> 18:58.670
taxes had been increasing in past years.

18:59.160 --> 19:02.190
The people's savings are like...

19:06.110 --> 19:07.640
like this wolf-hair brush.

19:08.030 --> 19:09.070
Normally,

19:09.070 --> 19:11.030
pulling out a few hairs is unnoticeable.

19:11.030 --> 19:12.510
But if you keep pulling,

19:12.510 --> 19:13.440
it becomes bald.

19:13.720 --> 19:15.320
Now, despite reduced taxes,

19:15.350 --> 19:16.480
the people are still

19:16.550 --> 19:18.310
wary of expanding their businesses.

19:18.310 --> 19:19.350
Why is that?

19:20.920 --> 19:22.250
Think about it, My Lord.

19:22.350 --> 19:23.360
At such a time,

19:23.790 --> 19:25.160
if we allocate special funds

19:25.160 --> 19:26.040
to the people,

19:26.350 --> 19:27.480
it's another story.

19:27.920 --> 19:29.000
The people's

19:29.000 --> 19:30.790
income will increase,

19:30.790 --> 19:31.830
and they will

19:31.830 --> 19:33.310
feel reassured.

19:33.310 --> 19:34.350
As such, they will

19:34.350 --> 19:37.240
spend more on food and clothing,
which stimulates farming and weaving,

19:37.240 --> 19:39.240
which leads to higher tax revenues.

19:39.440 --> 19:40.900
Therefore, I believe that

19:41.000 --> 19:42.190
such circulation is what

19:42.190 --> 19:45.790
truly fosters the nation's growth
and the people's prosperity.

19:47.360 --> 19:49.960
This will reasonably
mobilize all resources,

19:50.550 --> 19:52.750
ensuring every commoner
has food to eat

19:53.030 --> 19:54.360
and hope for the future.

19:54.480 --> 19:57.810
This is the very meaning of
my Commerce Bureau's existence.

19:59.320 --> 20:00.100
This is

20:00.710 --> 20:02.300
the subsidy system I drafted.

20:02.140 --> 20:02.780
[Subsidy System]

20:02.850 --> 20:04.300
Report it to the governor

20:04.510 --> 20:06.310
at tomorrow's morning assembly.

20:06.310 --> 20:07.030
Yes.

20:07.510 --> 20:08.480
Lord Jiang,

20:08.480 --> 20:09.400
so you

20:09.400 --> 20:11.030
already had this idea!

20:11.920 --> 20:14.650
There are many officials
in the Commerce Bureau,

20:14.830 --> 20:18.030
but there are very few
who truly understand the suffering

20:18.550 --> 20:19.790
of the common people.

20:25.960 --> 20:26.750
Fan Xiu,

20:26.900 --> 20:28.180
go to the Rites Bureau

20:28.830 --> 20:30.830
and return these documents as well.

20:31.920 --> 20:32.510
Yes.

20:38.440 --> 20:39.410
That young man is

20:39.920 --> 20:41.380
quite formidable indeed.

20:41.880 --> 20:42.600
It's a pity

20:42.930 --> 20:45.660
he's only temporarily assigned here
for a month.

21:11.030 --> 21:12.030
Your Excellency.

21:13.640 --> 21:14.510
Elders!

21:14.790 --> 21:15.520
You're here.

21:16.540 --> 21:18.020
You skipped the morning assembly

21:18.020 --> 21:19.510
to come here, Your Excellency?

21:19.510 --> 21:21.370
Is there no one to do these chores?

21:22.690 --> 21:23.450
Elder Zheng,

21:23.870 --> 21:25.130
I asked to do it myself.

21:25.720 --> 21:26.400
I thought I could

21:26.400 --> 21:27.820
experience the hardships of

21:27.820 --> 21:28.970
ordinary people by

21:29.000 --> 21:31.150
cultivating land in the estate's garden

21:31.150 --> 21:33.010
and growing some produce myself.

21:33.330 --> 21:34.130
Elders,

21:34.870 --> 21:36.130
care to join me?

21:36.400 --> 21:38.140
The governor and the ministers

21:38.160 --> 21:39.760
should not be do such things.

21:41.750 --> 21:42.400
It's fine.

21:42.400 --> 21:43.380
Be careful!

21:46.480 --> 21:48.260
The seedling that was just planted

21:48.260 --> 21:49.090
was crushed.

21:54.480 --> 21:56.110
You're right to reprimand me, Elder Zheng.

21:56.110 --> 21:56.910
I just thought

21:57.240 --> 21:58.500
that a governor should

21:58.680 --> 22:01.200
at least understand the basics of farming.

22:01.830 --> 22:02.830
As the saying goes,

22:02.830 --> 22:05.100
everyone has
their own strengths and weaknesses.

22:05.100 --> 22:07.210
If the Nine Cities want to prosper,

22:07.310 --> 22:09.110
we must pool our wisdom and efforts.

22:09.110 --> 22:10.550
Just now, while planting,

22:10.550 --> 22:12.000
I had an idea.

22:12.880 --> 22:14.010
How about modifying

22:14.410 --> 22:15.880
the selection exam

22:16.230 --> 22:17.100
into...

22:18.550 --> 22:19.810
a national selection?

22:23.920 --> 22:25.780
Wouldn't it be great if commoners

22:25.810 --> 22:27.540
could participate in the exam?

22:30.530 --> 22:32.240
A national selection?

22:32.370 --> 22:34.110
What are you trying to do,
Your Excellency?

22:34.110 --> 22:35.640
This is utterly unheard of.

22:36.150 --> 22:38.280
Did the Three Elders all agree to this?

22:40.830 --> 22:41.910
Your Excellency,

22:43.270 --> 22:44.380
I believe

22:45.960 --> 22:47.270
a national selection

22:47.690 --> 22:48.750
is inappropriate.

22:53.720 --> 22:54.630
How so?

22:55.640 --> 22:56.500
Nobles

22:56.770 --> 22:58.440
are nobles

22:59.160 --> 23:02.760
because their ancestors
made contributions to the Nine Cities.

23:02.850 --> 23:04.010
Their descendants

23:04.510 --> 23:07.270
read the best books from a young age,

23:07.880 --> 23:10.430
learning how to govern the people.

23:11.590 --> 23:13.160
But the commoners?

23:13.500 --> 23:14.790
They have no merits

23:14.810 --> 23:16.240
and are illiterate.

23:16.920 --> 23:19.230
Even if their descendants receive

23:19.260 --> 23:20.450
some education,

23:20.640 --> 23:21.460
they're still

23:22.550 --> 23:24.070
short-sighted

23:24.410 --> 23:26.090
and unversed in the ways of officialdom;

23:26.090 --> 23:27.850
just armchair strategists.

23:28.850 --> 23:30.650
If they're appointed to office,

23:31.550 --> 23:33.200
pushing out the real talents,

23:33.200 --> 23:34.250
won't the Nine Cities

23:34.250 --> 23:35.680
be thrown into chaos?

23:35.700 --> 23:36.280
But...

23:41.480 --> 23:44.200
We still should give
the people of the Nine Cities

23:44.200 --> 23:46.060
a chance to change their destiny,

23:46.200 --> 23:48.090
a chance to broaden their horizons.

23:48.090 --> 23:48.890
Only then

23:48.910 --> 23:51.180
can the people have hope.

23:51.210 --> 23:52.680
Only then will the Nine Cities have hope.

23:52.680 --> 23:54.710
Only when the people know their place

23:54.710 --> 23:56.510
will the Nine Cities have hope.

23:58.310 --> 24:01.550
Your Excellency,
are you trying to make the people

24:01.580 --> 24:03.510
dissatisfied with the status quo?

24:04.110 --> 24:05.440
I'm afraid this is

24:05.440 --> 24:08.790
a path of no return that will
spell the end of the Nine Cities.

24:10.750 --> 24:13.350
Please think twice, Your Excellency.

24:25.370 --> 24:26.370
Elder Zheng.

24:26.720 --> 24:28.240
I fooled you, didn't I?

24:28.270 --> 24:29.620
You all misheard.

24:29.870 --> 24:30.870
The talent selection exam

24:30.870 --> 24:33.130
is a monumental event of the Nine Cities.

24:33.230 --> 24:34.470
It's no child's play!

24:34.490 --> 24:36.830
All of the Nine Cities
must be mobilized for it!

24:36.830 --> 24:38.000
A national selection?

24:38.000 --> 24:39.050
It was just a joke.

24:39.070 --> 24:40.210
Of course not.

24:41.220 --> 24:42.330
Don't be angry.

24:45.310 --> 24:47.000
I hope I misheard.

24:47.020 --> 24:47.820
You misheard.

24:48.030 --> 24:50.000
Your Excellency, you must never

24:50.270 --> 24:52.170
act so absurdly again.

24:52.540 --> 24:53.310
Otherwise,

24:54.590 --> 24:57.160
it'll unsettle the ministers.

24:59.240 --> 25:00.640
I realize my mistake.

25:04.350 --> 25:05.350
Your Excellency,

25:06.550 --> 25:08.150
carry on with your planting.

25:15.200 --> 25:16.350
Let's go.

25:17.070 --> 25:17.920
Come on.

25:22.000 --> 25:23.100
Take care, Elders!

25:41.240 --> 25:43.810
Today, please tell me
where you each stand.

25:43.920 --> 25:47.900
Do you support the governor
opening the exam to everyone,

25:48.190 --> 25:50.390
or do you support me?

25:52.000 --> 25:53.110
Lyu,

25:54.030 --> 25:55.630
just give a straight answer.

26:07.590 --> 26:09.450
The three of us

26:09.750 --> 26:11.150
are one.

26:12.070 --> 26:13.750
When have we ever disagreed?

26:17.670 --> 26:18.600
I feel the same!

26:20.310 --> 26:21.180
Zheng,

26:21.590 --> 26:24.790
you're resolved to protect
the Nine Cities' foundation.

26:25.400 --> 26:27.110
You have my full commitment!

26:29.680 --> 26:30.630
Mine too!

26:34.400 --> 26:35.720
I'm gratified that

26:35.960 --> 26:37.460
you two feel this way.

26:38.720 --> 26:41.070
I hope what you just said

26:41.580 --> 26:43.060
is what you really think.

26:43.090 --> 26:44.300
You must not

26:44.610 --> 26:46.570
go back on your words.

26:46.590 --> 26:47.660
Of course not.

26:47.690 --> 26:48.620
Absolutely not.

26:48.720 --> 26:49.780
Of course we won't.

26:58.330 --> 26:59.360
Here, here.

27:29.450 --> 27:30.690
Not bad.

27:31.810 --> 27:32.690
Fan Xiu.

27:34.450 --> 27:35.970
What are you doing?

27:36.040 --> 27:36.770
Lord Jiang.

27:37.310 --> 27:38.240
I'm classifying

27:38.440 --> 27:40.240
the processed documents.

27:40.920 --> 27:42.030
Classifying them?

27:42.250 --> 27:43.250
Lord Jiang, look,

27:43.420 --> 27:46.260
I've numbered all the documents
of the Commerce Bureau.

27:46.260 --> 27:48.320
It'll be easier to review them later.

27:49.200 --> 27:50.250
Then tell me

27:50.730 --> 27:52.150
how you numbered them.

27:52.170 --> 27:54.060
I divided them into 3 levels.

27:54.090 --> 27:55.000
The first level

27:55.020 --> 27:55.910
is by bureau.

27:56.150 --> 27:56.980
The second level

27:56.980 --> 27:58.090
is by city.

27:58.120 --> 27:59.050
The third level

27:59.070 --> 28:00.420
is by year.

28:01.070 --> 28:03.510
This makes it easy
to quickly locate documents

28:03.510 --> 28:05.770
when each bureau comes to retrieve them.

28:06.310 --> 28:07.710
This method is feasible,

28:08.000 --> 28:10.530
but how would we look up records

28:10.560 --> 28:11.980
of the same city

28:12.390 --> 28:13.700
for a specific date?

28:14.110 --> 28:15.220
Don't worry, Lord Jiang.

28:15.220 --> 28:16.750
I also made a few tables

28:16.880 --> 28:19.040
corresponding to time, region,

28:19.060 --> 28:20.260
and expense details.

28:22.880 --> 28:25.640
So, you've finished your 3 days' work?

28:27.740 --> 28:29.100
I... I...

28:29.130 --> 28:30.440
Not yet,

28:30.550 --> 28:31.920
but I'm almost done.

28:34.410 --> 28:35.340
Then keep going.

28:36.140 --> 28:36.860
Yes.

28:36.890 --> 28:38.090
I'll do it right away.

29:15.310 --> 29:18.270
"Only when... Only when..."

29:18.550 --> 29:21.510
"Only when the state is well-governed
will the world be at peace.

29:21.510 --> 29:23.710
From the head of state to the common man,

29:24.510 --> 29:27.370
self-cultivation is
the root of one's foundation.

29:27.750 --> 29:29.660
If the root is in disorder,
the branches can't be

29:29.660 --> 29:30.590
well-governed.

29:31.160 --> 29:33.120
Failing to distinguish and prioritize

29:33.120 --> 29:34.850
the essential from the trivial

29:35.700 --> 29:37.630
has catastrophic repercussions.

29:38.240 --> 29:39.760
The preceding chapter of Classic

29:39.760 --> 29:41.550
consists of the words of Confucius,

29:41.550 --> 29:43.440
as recorded by Zengzi.

29:43.700 --> 29:44.890
The next 10 chapters of commentary

29:44.890 --> 29:48.090
convey the ideas of Zengzi,
as recorded by his disciples.

29:48.270 --> 29:50.800
The old editions contain
quite a few errors."

29:53.330 --> 29:54.130
Grandfather?

29:54.290 --> 29:55.200
Sit.

29:59.350 --> 30:01.010
Drink the ginseng soup first.

30:01.220 --> 30:02.260
It'll get cold.

30:02.640 --> 30:03.230
OK.

30:06.170 --> 30:07.620
Look at my grandson.

30:08.400 --> 30:10.460
This is what a noble should look like.

30:11.200 --> 30:13.460
So hardworking and outstanding.

30:14.070 --> 30:15.070
He will

30:15.100 --> 30:16.780
bring honor to our family.

30:17.640 --> 30:19.370
He is the only chosen one

30:19.790 --> 30:21.750
to safeguard the Nine Cities.

30:31.400 --> 30:32.290
Grandfather.

30:33.770 --> 30:35.640
If my exam results aren't satisfactory...

30:35.640 --> 30:36.840
How could that be?

30:38.270 --> 30:39.670
Look how capable you are.

30:39.720 --> 30:40.960
I have great confidence

30:40.960 --> 30:43.130
in your abilities.

30:43.590 --> 30:44.520
However,

30:45.920 --> 30:48.030
don't work too hard.

30:48.030 --> 30:49.350
Exhausting yourself

30:49.350 --> 30:51.200
will affect your performance.

30:52.290 --> 30:53.290
-Yes.
-And…

30:54.880 --> 30:57.140
You should rest early too, Grandfather.

30:58.980 --> 31:00.070
Right. OK.

31:58.850 --> 32:00.520
How did I fall asleep?

32:03.750 --> 32:05.460
You... You...

32:05.550 --> 32:06.550
Your Excellency?

32:07.440 --> 32:08.640
Why are you here?

32:09.590 --> 32:11.440
Then... Where is Lord Jiang?

32:12.270 --> 32:13.100
Fan Xiu.

32:13.960 --> 32:16.480
You must be having fun
at the Commerce Bureau.

32:16.480 --> 32:18.680
Spending day and night with Lord Jiang,

32:18.900 --> 32:20.300
you even dream about him.

33:07.750 --> 33:08.440
I...

33:08.810 --> 33:10.640
It's because I've been busy

33:10.670 --> 33:12.430
from morning until just now.

33:12.550 --> 33:14.060
Once I relaxed,

33:14.100 --> 33:15.370
I fell asleep.

33:17.030 --> 33:18.030
How is it?

33:18.750 --> 33:20.400
Are you enjoying your apprenticeship

33:20.400 --> 33:21.730
at the Commerce Bureau?

33:25.070 --> 33:26.330
It's been pretty good.

33:53.640 --> 33:54.710
It's getting late.

33:55.070 --> 33:56.200
I should go home.

33:56.550 --> 33:57.550
Your Excellency,

33:57.550 --> 33:58.350
you should

33:58.350 --> 33:59.810
go back and rest early too.

34:00.110 --> 34:00.650
I...

34:02.560 --> 34:04.160
This place belongs to me too.

34:07.350 --> 34:08.190
Right.

34:08.770 --> 34:09.889
Then I'll...

34:10.480 --> 34:11.739
I'll take my leave now.

34:14.239 --> 34:15.699
But it's pouring outside.

34:19.500 --> 34:20.830
That scared me to death.

34:43.790 --> 34:44.460
Fan Yun!

34:45.190 --> 34:46.480
I know you miss me a lot.

34:46.880 --> 34:47.560
But...

34:48.710 --> 34:49.760
Let go of me.

34:49.969 --> 34:51.260
You're hurting my ribs.

34:50.540 --> 34:52.429
♪ Why oh why ♪

34:51.280 --> 34:53.150
What are you doing, Your Excellency?

34:52.460 --> 34:53.739
♪ Is the path of destiny ♪

34:53.610 --> 34:55.889
You're the one squeezing my ribs.

34:53.760 --> 34:56.389
♪ So bittersweet? ♪

34:56.630 --> 34:57.480
I... I...

34:57.130 --> 34:59.030
♪ My gaze rests on ♪

34:57.480 --> 34:58.710
Your Excellency!

34:59.060 --> 35:03.210
♪ The fading lights,
with nowhere to return ♪

35:00.710 --> 35:02.590
Why are you so strong?

35:02.590 --> 35:03.550
You...

35:03.230 --> 35:06.780
♪ Inundated with bitter pain ♪

35:05.240 --> 35:06.000
I...

35:06.820 --> 35:09.220
I'm just scared of thunder.

35:07.610 --> 35:10.100
♪ My obsession still wouldn't surrender ♪

35:10.840 --> 35:16.500
♪ In the end,
my love is still unrequited ♪

35:13.440 --> 35:15.440
You're actually scared of thunder?

35:17.820 --> 35:19.290
♪ I could have ♪

35:19.320 --> 35:20.920
♪ Played every trick in the book ♪

35:20.940 --> 35:24.300
♪ But I chose painstaking devotion ♪

35:21.240 --> 35:22.170
Don't be afraid.

35:22.820 --> 35:24.010
I'm here.

35:24.480 --> 35:26.140
♪ Never caging my love ♪

35:26.160 --> 35:30.390
♪ Even if I had to
trudge through a thousand miles ♪

35:30.510 --> 35:34.590
♪ Henceforth, I shall wander the world,
plucking petals and holding the moon ♪

35:34.850 --> 35:38.160
♪ Listen to the wind and admire the moon
for days on end ♪

35:38.340 --> 35:44.260
♪ Accept that I'm not your happiness ♪

35:44.340 --> 35:47.050
♪ Let go of what's before me ♪

35:47.080 --> 35:51.040
♪ Consider this the best ending ♪

35:51.150 --> 35:53.640
♪ I disdain everything
in the vast universe ♪

35:53.660 --> 35:58.020
♪ So why do I care for
a single glance from you? ♪

35:58.040 --> 36:00.680
♪ Drinking a pot of the past ♪

36:00.700 --> 36:05.550
♪ I toast to my withering self
as the curtains fall ♪

36:03.020 --> 36:05.500
Why is there an umbrella here?

36:05.580 --> 36:11.800
♪ And you don't know the reason why ♪

36:05.590 --> 36:06.960
Did you leave it here?

36:11.190 --> 36:12.060
Let's go.

36:12.450 --> 36:13.540
I'll walk you home.

36:17.840 --> 36:18.690
Let's go.
